    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short, thick arrows fitted with flights and a head of any of various shapes, often square or blunt, designed to be shot by crossbows.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
